o independent implementations, a finite-difference one\nand a spectral one. We discuss the extension of our method to a full 3D\nnumerical evolution and to gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Sep 2021 10:24:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-09"}
