el is utilized\nto obtain the optimal transmission rate for the IoT devices that minimizes\ndelay. The numerical results delineate the joint feasibility range of packet\nsizes and inter-arrival times for data aggregation and reveal significant gains\nwhen deploying directional antennas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Sep 2021 11:52:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-09"}
