pace $X$ is isometric to the maximal\nGromov product space $\\mathcal{M}(Z)$, where $Z$ is the boundary of $X$. We\nalso show that a Gromov product space is injective if and only if it is\nmaximal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Sep 2021 15:34:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 08:13:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 20:29:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
